data.description: Welcome Home to Bexley!  This fantastic 2-story home is tucked away in a cul-de-sac ready for new homeowners. A highly sought-after home welcomes you in with a lovely covered front porch. Upon entering into the home, you are instantly captivated by a beautiful spacious formal dining room. An open concept living area and kitchen continue to invite you in with granitic countertops, deep cabinets, kitchen island.  Elegant wood stairs lead you up to 4 bedrooms, 2 baths and roomy open loft. The backyard is facing a lush tree line which provides privacy and serenity. Enjoy the comforts of South Carolina taxes.
